title: "Spatial-Matrix Agentic Toolkit"
abstract: 
  The MatrixEngine® Agentic Toolkit allows you to use AI agents with MatrixEngine 
  by giving your AI agent the knowledge and context to work efficiently 
  with MatrixEngine and its toolboxes. Use this toolkit to provide trusted 
  MatrixEngine capabilities to your agent.

